OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781384336
OL,3,CInvestigation into 1996 bombing closed
OL,4,Cby counter terrorism police
OL,6,FCounter Terrorism Police have closed
OL,7,Fthe investigation into the biggest
OL,8,Fbomb planted on the UK mainland and
OL,9,Fclaimed by the IRA ahead of the 30th
OL,10,Fanniversary of the attack.
OL,12,FA review was launched a decade ago
OL,13,Finto the Manchester Arndale bombing to
OL,14,Fsee if new techniques or information
OL,15,Fcould aid the investigation.
OL,17,FBut detectives from Counter Terrorism
OL,18,FPolicing North West now say all lines
OL,19,Fof enquiry have been exhausted, in a
OL,20,Fstatement released on 11 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
