PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781384336
OL,3,CInvestigation into 1996 bombing closed
OL,4,Cby counter terrorism police
OL,6,FA man was arrested at Birmingham
OL,7,Fairport in September 2022, and
OL,8,Freleased without charge after
OL,9,Finterview.
OL,11,FPolice say another man would have been
OL,12,Farrested and interviewed, but he died
OL,13,Fseveral years ago, before an arrest
OL,14,Fcould take place.
OL,16,FTwo IRA members planted the biggest
OL,17,Fbomb on the UK mainland since World
OL,18,FWar Two targeting shoppers at the
OL,19,FManchester Arndale shopping centre on
OL,20,FSaturday 15 June 1996.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
