FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781384336
OL,3,CInvestigation into 1996 bombing closed
OL,4,Cby counter terrorism police
OL,6,FIt caused extensive damage and an
OL,7,Fevacuation, but no-one was killed. 200
OL,8,Fpeople were injured and many were left
OL,9,Ftraumatised by the attack.
OL,11,FThe attack came on a sunny Saturday
OL,12,Fbefore Fathers Day, as the Arndale
OL,13,FCentre was packed with shoppers.
OL,14,FFootball fans were also in town for
OL,15,Fthe next day's Russia v Germany
OL,16,Ffixture at nearby Old Trafford.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
