FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781384336
OL,3,CInvestigation into 1996 bombing closed
OL,4,Cby counter terrorism police
OL,6,FBomb disposal officers attempted to
OL,7,Fdefuse the explosive with a remote-
OL,8,Fcontrolled robot.
OL,10,FThe attempt failed and, at 11.17am,
OL,11,Fthe 3,300lb device exploded. Smoke
OL,12,Fmushroomed high above the city while
OL,13,Fbuildings shook and glass shattered,
OL,14,Fraining debris on people outside the
OL,15,Fcordoned area.
OL,17,FAssistant Chief Constable Rob Potts
OL,18,Fsaid: "The 1996 Manchester bombing was
OL,19,Fa significant event in the history of
OL,20,Fthe city of Manchester and beyond.
OL,26,@zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781384336
OL,3,CInvestigation into 1996 bombing closed
OL,4,Cby counter terrorism police
OL,6,F"Many of us can tell you exactly where
OL,7,Fwe were and what we were doing when
OL,8,Fthe bomb exploded.
OL,10,F"The impact of the explosion was so
OL,11,Flarge that the city centre
OL,12,Farchitecture physically changed
OL,13,Fforever. It is close to a miracle that
OL,14,Fnobody was killed during the incident;
OL,15,Fhowever, hundreds of people were
OL,16,Fphysically injured, and many more were
OL,17,Falso profoundly impacted by what
OL,18,Fhappened on that day.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781384336
OL,3,CInvestigation into 1996 bombing closed
OL,4,Cby counter terrorism police
OL,6,F"It is for that reason that we have
OL,7,Fbeen committed to establishing the
OL,8,Ffull picture behind what happened and
OL,9,Fhave continued to review this case,
OL,10,Fdespite the passage of time since.
OL,12,F"Following the 20th anniversary, we
OL,13,Ftook the decision to conduct a review
OL,14,Fof the original investigation and all
OL,15,Fthe available evidence. This
OL,16,Fidentified some new, albeit limited,
OL,17,Finvestigative opportunities.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781384336
OL,3,CInvestigation into 1996 bombing closed
OL,4,Cby counter terrorism police
OL,6,F"A case of this significance, coupled
OL,7,Fwith the amount of time that has
OL,8,Fpassed, brings complexities so
OL,9,Fpursuing limited investigative
OL,10,Fopportunities such as these takes
OL,11,Ftime. We arrested and interviewed one
OL,12,Fsuspect in 2022 before releasing him
OL,13,Fwithout charge. A second man would
OL,14,Fhave been arrested and interviewed;
OL,15,Fhowever he died whilst preparations
OL,16,Fwere underway to arrest him.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
