PN,39809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1781384336
OL,3,CInvestigation into 1996 bombing closed
OL,4,Cby counter terrorism police
OL,6,F"Those limited investigative
OL,7,Fopportunities have now been exhausted
OL,8,Fand the investigation is no longer
OL,9,Factive. Should any further evidence or
OL,10,Finformation come to light about new or
OL,11,Fexisting suspects then we are prepared
OL,12,Fto review this position again."
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@_O]
